    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>*<persName key="#Bishops #Popes #Papal_concession" ref="#people/51">Innocentius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Popes">servus servorum</rs> Dei dilecto filio <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries #Intercessory #Papal_concession" ref="#people/3568"
                            >Henrico</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Papal_concession #Churches #Decima #Agricultural_workers #Public_exactions #Fodrum" ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti
                            Benedicti super Padum</orgName> eiusque* successoribus regulariter
                        substituendis in perpetuum. In apostolice sedis specula disponente domino
                        constituti ecclesiarum omnium curam nos convenit gerere et ad earum quietem
                        et pacem omnimodis laborare. Proinde dilecte in domino fili Henrice abbas
                        tuis rationabilibus <rs key="#Intercessory">postulationibus</rs> clementer
                        annuimus, atque <orgName key="#Churches #Decima #Agricultural_workers #Public_exactions #Fodrum" ref="#juridical_persons/2068"><rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> de <placeName key="#Churches #Decima #Agricultural_workers #Public_exactions #Fodrum"
                                ref="#places/77">Ficarolo</placeName>
                        </orgName>cum <rs key="#Decima">decimis</rs> illius partis, quam a tuis <rs
                            key="#Agricultural_workers">colonis</rs> percipis, ab omni <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">exactione</rs> et <rs key="#Fodrum">fodro</rs>
                        cum omnibus suis hominibus ad eam pertinentibus liberam esse decernimus, et
                        in nulla uolumus eam libertate consistere, quam iam dudum ipsa noscitur
                        habuisse. Salvo nimirum iure et iustitia <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1100">Sanctę Romanę ęcclesię</orgName>.
                        Statuimus itaque ut nulli omnino hominum liceat hanc <rs
                            key="#Papal_concession">nostra constitutionem seu confirmatione</rs>
                        infringere vel mutare aut prefatam ecclesiam seu homines ad ipsam
                        pertinentes cum decimis suis temerariis vexationibus fatigare. Si quis autem
                        hoc ausu temerario attemptare presumpserit indignationem Dei ornnipotentis
                        et beatorum Petri et Pauli apostolorum eius incurrat. + Ego Innocentius
                        Catholice ecclesię episcopus SS. + Ego <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/3712"
                            >Conradus</persName>
                        <orgName key="#Bishops #Papal_concession #Witness" ref="#juridical_persons/2458">Sabine</orgName> episcopus <rs key="#Witness">SS.</rs> Datum <placeName key="#Papal_concession"
                            ref="#places/66">Pisis</placeName> per manum <persName
                                ref="#people/3563" key="#Deacons #Cardinals #Chancellor #Papal_concession"
                            >Aimerici</persName>, Sancte Romane Ecclesia <rs key="#Deacons"
                            >Diaconus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cardinals">Cardinalis</rs> et <rs key="#Chancellor"
                            >Cancellarius</rs>, VII Kalendas novembris. Indictione prima.
                        Incarnationis Dominice anno M.C.XXXVIIJ. Pontificatus vero Domini Innocentii
                        pape II. Anno VIIIJ. </ab>
